title: Delta Media Player 1.20 2018 [PL]
description:
DESCRIPTION ========= ========

Delta media Player (Available on PC, MAC OS, LINUX, Android)

DeltaMediaPlayer provides a new generation of online television services.
127 channels will be available for viewing on a computer or laptop.
Lots of news, music, sports, entertainment for children, and other channels will be available to you 24/7.
Programs are broadcast in high image and sound quality. (HD, SD)
To be able to watch programs on the Internet on your computer, you will need to install DeltaMediaPlayer.
Some player features include:
List of channels, updated daily
EPG, schedule of television programs

TOGETHER almost 130 channels (including all HBO, Canal +, Discovery and etc.)


INSTALLATION ========= ========
Description of the installation in the middle of the insert
